//NAME
<jaN0001>Ryota
<enN0001>Ryota

//NAME
<jaN0002>Shuhei
<enN0002>Shuhei

//NAME
<jaN0003>Scarred Man
<enN0003>Scarred Man

///================================================================================

//TEXT
<jaT0001>A tempest of high speed rifle bullets fired on full auto.
<enT0001>A tempest of high speed rifle bullets fired on full auto.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0002>"Uwah!"
<enT0002>"Uwah!"

//TEXT
<jaT0003>Ryota's shield just barely managed to repel the bullets, but his arm couldn't take it. He dropped the shield under the intense pressure and fell backwards devoid of strength.
<enT0003>Ryota's shield just barely managed to repel the bullets, but his arm couldn't take it. He dropped the shield under the intense pressure and fell backwards devoid of strength.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0004>"Ryota!"
<enT0004>"Ryota!"

//TEXT
<jaT0005>I leapt out into the center of the hall, gun in hand, trying to protect the defenseless Ryota.
<enT0005>I leapt out into the center of the hall, gun in hand, trying to protect the defenseless Ryota.

//TEXT 【Scarred Man】
<jaT0006>"Who the hell are you?!"
<enT0006>"Who the hell are you?!"

//TEXT
<jaT0007>The man was undisturbed by the appearance of a new target. He simply fired his assault rifle one handed again.
<enT0007>The man was undisturbed by the appearance of a new target. He simply fired his assault rifle one handed again.

//TEXT
<jaT0008>He had no aim, but there was nothing I could do against that semi-auto rifle.
<enT0008>He had no aim, but there was nothing I could do against that semi-auto rifle.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0009>"Dammit!!"
<enT0009>"Dammit!!"

//TEXT
<jaT0010>I tried to pull the trigger, but bullets ripped through my arms. The next instant, my chest, my neck, and my head were turned into a honeycomb.
<enT0010>I tried to pull the trigger, but bullets ripped through my arms. The next instant, my chest, my neck, and my head were turned into a honeycomb.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>I didn't even have time to feel pain. My consciousness just sank directly into darkness...
<enT0011>I didn't even have time to feel pain. My consciousness just sank directly into darkness...

//TEXT
<jaT0012>......
<enT0012>......

//TEXT
